source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_00<tab>The Allagan life support node's status light is blinking an ominous red...
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_00<tab>第IV転送リング付近の保全システムは、静かに佇んでいる。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_01<tab>The Allagan life support node informs you that atmospheric levels of corpse flower spores are at critically dangerous levels─and rising. Destroy corpse flowers to reduce the release of these apparently dangerous pollutants.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_01<tab>保全システムによると、<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>によって大気が汚染されているらしい。アジス・ラーのベータ管区にいる「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>」を4体討伐しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_02<tab>You extirpate the troublesome corpse flowers. Return to the life support node to confirm that there are no other sources of dangerous atmospheric contaminants.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>を倒した。第IV転送リング付近の「保全システム」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_03<tab>With the reduced rate of spore output, the life support system is now able to purify the air faster than it is being polluted. The abnormally high corpse flower population seems to have been caused by an airborne growth stimulation medium released from the ecological synthesis research facility.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_SEQ_03<tab>保全システムに報告した。胞子の異常放出は、<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>が合成生物用の培養液を吸い上げたことが原因だったそうだ。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_TODO_01<tab>Report to the life support node.

TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_000<tab>Atmospheric impurities at critical levels. Atmospheric corpse flower spore levels currently at one thousand three hundred and twelve percent of maximum safe limit and rising.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_000<tab>ザ……ザザ……付近一帯の空気に異常な量の胞子を確認。
<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>から放出したものと思われます。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_001<tab>Immediate destruction of corpse flowers is highly recommended to ensure citizen safety.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_001<tab>大気汚染が進行しています。
すみやかに「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>」を駆除してください。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_010<tab>Immediate destruction of corpse flowers is highly recommended to ensure continued citizen safety.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_010<tab>大気汚染が進行しています。
すみやかに「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>」を駆除してください。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_020<tab>Atmospheric corpse flower spore levels currently at one thousand three hundred and eleven percent of maximum safe limit and falling.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_020<tab>ザ……ザザ……<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F20DD601 /var>の反応消失を確認。
お疲れさまでした。

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_021<tab>Increased corpse flower population determined to be a result of atmospheric growth stimulation catalyst being unintentionally released by the ecological synthesis research facility. Transmitting report to research facility... <blip> <blip> Transmission complete.
target:
TEXT_HEAVNZ919_01984_CONSERVATIONSYSTEM_000_021<tab>胞子の異常放出は、対象が、
合成生物用の培養液を吸い上げたことが原因と判明。
キメラ生成ラボにレポートを提出します……ザザ……。
